         MACRO
         QCBD
* QUEUE CONTROL BLOCK (QCB) DEFINITION
         SPACE
QBLOCK   DSECT
QKEY     DS    FL1 QUEUE STATUS AS --
*                                   1=NOT ON READY QUEUE
*                                   2=NOT WAITING (I.E. READY)
*                                   3=WAITING
QFAC     DS    AL3  ADDR OF 1ST ELEMENT ON ELEMENT CHAIN
         SPACE
QPRI     DS    FL1  READY QUEUE PRIORITY FOR QCB
QLINK    DS    AL3 ADDR OF NEXT ITEM ON RDY Q WHEN QCB IS ON RDY Q
QTRAN    DS    FL1 UNUSED UNLESS QCB COMBINED WITH STCB = RETURN CODE
         DS    AL3 ADDR OF FIRST STCB ON QUEUE
         SPACE
*        WHEN TRUNCATED STCB IS COMBINED WITH QCB
         ORG   QBLOCK+8
         DS    FL1 STCB RETURN CODE
         DS    AL3 ADDR OF FIRST STCB ON QCB'S STCB CHAIN
         DS    XL1  STCB PRIORITY
         DS    AL3 ADDR OF NEXT STCB ON CHAIN
         SPACE
*  ADDITIONAL INFO FOR DASD DESTINATION QUEUE
QRLN     DS    FL1  RELATIVE LINE NUMBER
QDCB     DS    AL3  ADDR OF DCB FOR THIS QCB
QSIZE    DS    H    NUMBER OF MESSAGES ON QUEUE
QNASEG   DS    AL3  ADDR OF AREA INTO WHICH NEXT SEG IS TO BE READ
QSORCE   DS    AL3  ADDR OF 1ST LCB ON LCB CHAIN
QDUMMY   DS    FL1  ALWAYS ZERO
QBACK    DS    AL3  DISK ADDR OF LAST MESSAGE PUT INTO THIS QUEUE
         MEND
